[graph] uses include graph (file -> file dependencies via `uses`) + build order
[graph] namespaces (declared-in / imported-by):
[graph]   A
[graph]     declared-in: a.ext
[graph]     imported-by: b.ext, main.ext
[graph]   B
[graph]     declared-in: b.ext
[graph]     imported-by: a.ext
[graph] file dependencies (A -> B: A `uses` a namespace B declares):
[graph]   a.ext -> b.ext
[graph]   b.ext -> a.ext
[graph]   main.ext -> a.ext
[graph] cycles: 
[graph]   { a.ext, b.ext }
[graph] build order: a.ext, b.ext, main.ext
